caller_intent: The caller wants to pay her rental home insurance policy online using a credit card and obtain a confirmation number.
resolution_steps: Agent verified the caller's policy details (rental home at 607 West Main Street, Pilot) and confirmed the outstanding balance ($965.30).
Agent processed the payment using the caller's First Citizens Bank Visa card (number provided).
Agent confirmed the card's expiration date (1/29) and verified the caller's email (GAW28@Hotmail.com).
Agent generated and provided a confirmation number (314-7773-7274) via phone after temporarily pausing the call to write it down.
summary: Marilyn Weaver successfully paid her rental home insurance policy online using a Visa card. The agent verified policy details, processed the payment, and provided a confirmation number. The caller confirmed no further assistance was needed.
